    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive example of the A80 platform. This specimen features the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, maintaining factory-spec compression across all cylinders with zero fluid seepage. Power is managed via the Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential, providing visceral mechanical feedback. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining all original VIN stickers on body panels and factory-correct double-wishbone suspension components. The interior is devoid of typical bolster wear, and the sequential turbocharging system transitions seamlessly without boost lag. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands mechanical purity and provenance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
