    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly collector-grade specimen that defines the term 'mint.' The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, mirror-like luster free of swirls, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather is supple and uncreased, the carpets are pristine under original mats, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. Mechanically, it is superlative, boasting a full binder of documented service history from authorized specialists, including a recent comprehensive fluid flush and multi-point inspection. Included are both original keys, the factory window sticker, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key vehicle that looks and performs exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
